<HEADLINE>
<P>
PRO FOOTBALL DAILY REPORT; AROUND THE NFL; COWBOYS' LASSIC LIKELY TO MISS 
SEASON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
