<P>
 Pentagon Approves General Dynamics Submarine: The decision means the company's 
Electric Boat Division in Groton, Conn., will have new attack submarines to 
build once it completes work on a second $2.5-billion Navy Seawolf, the company 
said.The project could be worth at least $60 billion to the company, it said. 
