<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY: OTHER NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Abbey Fires Executives: The company said it has fired several executives who 
were part of former President Victor M.G. Chaltiel's management team.Abbey 
Healthcare Group Inc., a Costa Mesa nursing home operator, would not identify 
the executives, but analysts said they are probably people in financial 
management posts within Abbey and its Total Pharmaceutical Care subsidiary. 
Chaltiel was head of Torrance-based Total Pharmaceutical when it was acquired 
by Abbey last year. He became Abbey's president as part of the deal. 
</P>
</TEXT>
