 IHOP Corp., the Glendale-based chain of International House of Pancake 
restaurants, reported record earnings for the second quarter ended June 30. 
</P>
<P>
 IHOP's net income was $3.7 million, up 170% from earnings of $1.37 million 
reported for the same three-month period a year ago.The second quarter results 
of 1993 included a non-recurring charge of $2.5 million related to litigation, 
