</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By FRANK MESSINA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Chamber of Commerce is seeking help to run the city's annual San Clemente 
Fiesta. 
</P>
<P>
 Volunteers are needed to make a diverse slate of events run smoothly, from the 
Fiesta 5000 run to the street festival on Avenida del Mar. 
</P>
<P>
