<TEXT>
<P>
 The Citadel may shave Shannon Faulkner's head when she becomes the first woman 
to join the school's corps of cadets, a judge ruled Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 U.S. District Judge C. Weston Houck also ordered Faulkner to stay in a private 
room in the college's infirmary instead of its barracks.And he rejected her 
