FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Appointment -- A story Thursday incorrectly described the process by which 
Marilyn Artran was appointed to the Los Angeles County Commission on 
Disabilities. Artran's appointment was made by Supervisor Michael Antonovich 
and approved by the Board of Supervisors. 
</P>
